em.research.elemingot.text=By throwing thaumium into crucible with elemental aspects you created strange metal - it rapidly changing colors, when you created tools of it they achive interesting properties -  pickaxe will give you haste, sword will give you strength, shovel will mine 3x3, axe will break wood from top, hoe will plow 3x3. All properties activated via right click. Howewer you cannot create aromor out of this metal, it will lose all properties. You can also make blocks of it.<BR>You also managed to create a shard, that works just like balanced shard, but with elemental primals only.
