tc.research_text.autodecomp=Soulbound
em.research.autodecomp.text=Elemental metal has another interesting property: it remembers man who last touched it. By adding variouns components you are able to create "Bound matrix", it will "write a link" to your mind if you touch it. This allows you to create a device that will work just like deconstructioun table, but instead of storing aspects it will transfer it directly to your mind. Howewer that link is weak, and aspect may corrupt when transfering, the greater distance will lead to more chace of corrupting. Corrupted aspects are useless and will only give you warp.
